<emphasis id="ACF3EAD7836F1F48FA7DF99CFEE3F9DD" box="[264,366,1556,1581]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Remarks</emphasis>
. The identity of this species was clarified by 
<bibRefCitation id="FA164B34836F1F48F8C0F99CFB16F9DE" author="Galil" box="[949,1179,1556,1582]" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" refString="Galil, B. (1988 b) Trapeziidae (Decapoda: Brachyura: Xanthoidea) of the Red Sea. Israel Journal of Zoology, 34, 159 - 182. [dated 1986 / 87]." type="journal article" year="1988" yearSuffix="b">
